# /pm — Project Management

Route based on arguments:
- No args → show status (call `pm_status`)
- `status` → detailed status dashboard
- `create story "<title>" "<description>"` → create a new story
- `create task <story-id> "<title>" "<description>"` → create a task
- `get <id>` → show item details
- `search <query>` → search items
- `update <id> <field>=<value>` → update an item
- `archive <id>` → archive an item

Use the ProjectMan MCP server tools to fulfill these requests. Present results in clean, readable format.
